  <name>Update Center</name>
  <summary>Manage all system updates in one place</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      GNOME Update Center provides a unified interface for managing all kinds of system updates.
      It combines software updates, firmware updates, driver installation, and repository management
      in a user-friendly interface.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Software updates through PackageKit</li>
      <li>Firmware updates via fwupd</li>
      <li>Hardware driver detection and installation</li>
      <li>Repository management</li>
      <li>Update scheduling and policy configuration</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
